She was a mender - a seamer, yes, seam - she used to seam. Because - when - when I was young - when we lived up Sherbrook Road - she used to come down to I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5064817 &}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3877088\charrsid9724261  R Morleys - for a bundle of - stockings or socks, and I used to have to sit and seam as well. I used to have to do the feet.
