rs. Well my Aunt Ri - Maria looked after the - elder children more you see. And - then when - then when we came along I mean - no, I think you used to have to look after yourself more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5064817 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3877088\charrsid9724261 Or your sisters look after you?
