ey'd - be at work and they'd come home for lunch and so you'd get your lunch - when they did you see. And - then you'd have to go out and play and - make your own arrangements until mother came home. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5064817 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3877088\charrsid9724261 How many rooms were there in the house in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
