{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Edwin Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} that used to be. Yes. And - excuse me, my - my uncle - he used to - have a save up, he worked in - he worked as a gardener for - at I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5064817 &}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3877088\charrsid9724261 
 R Morleys, and at - the Cedars - hospital before it was the Cedars. He used to work there as a gardener. And he'd save all his money up and he wouldn't spend any for about six months, and then he'd take my - niece and me and buy
 us a new pair of shoes. Always had new shoes, yes.
