{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Jacksons{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. At Daybrook, he used to live - on the other side from the - the bureau, you know where the bureau works on, he used to live in a - little cottage there.
\par 
