People often tell us in those days that they made their own amusements, what do you think your parents did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5064817 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3877088\charrsid9724261 You told me you actually went to school when you were two and a half?
