e - the they didn't you see and then - well not 'til then but - anyway it - mother said, well now she's started you mustn't stop her because, she says, she will be with - where George is you see. So he said, no, it's all right Mrs Archer, he said, only - 
I - it's - it's terrible really, he said, two and a half and she's such a big girl.
